General Context
The project is a full-stack IoT Dashboard to monitor devices and sensor data.

Stack:
Frontend: React (with Vite), Bootstrap, CSS Modules

Backend: Node.js + Express

Database: MongoDB Atlas

Auth: Google OAuth + Email/Password (JWT, now via HTTP-only cookies)

Hosting: Azure App Service (Linux)
